<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Administrator Access — PT. Trimas Mitra Perkasa</title>
    <link href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root { --steel: #2a7ab8; --accent: #f47320; }
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: #060e1a; min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 80%, rgba(42,122,184,0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
                              radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(15,45,82,0.3) 0%, transparent 40%);
        }
        .login-wrap { display: flex; max-width: 820px; width: 100%; gap: 2rem; align-items: center; }

        /* Left info panel */
        .login-info { flex: 1; padding: 1rem; display: none; }
        @media (min-width: 768px) { .login-info { display: block; } }
        .info-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .info-logo-icon {
            width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 10px;
            background: rgba(42,122,184,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(42,122,184,0.25);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.1rem; color: #60a5fa;
        }
        .info-logo-name { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; }
        .info-logo-sub  { font-size: 0.72rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); }
        .info-title { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
        .info-title span { color: #60a5fa; }
        .info-desc { font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .info-features { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
        .info-features li {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem;
            font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
            margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
        }
        .info-features li i { color: #60a5fa; width: 14px; }

        /* Login card */
        .login-card {
            background: #0d1f33;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
            border-radius: 16px;
            width: 100%; max-width: 380px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .card-eyebrow {
            font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.2px;
            text-transform: uppercase; color: #60a5fa;
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
        }
        .card-title { font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
        .card-sub { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); margin-bottom: 2rem; }

        .form-label-dark {
            font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
            display: block; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
        }
        .input-dark {
            width: 100%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09); color: #fff;
            border-radius: 9px; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: all 0.2s; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        .input-dark:focus {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            border-color: var(--steel); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(42,122,184,0.15);
            outline: none; color: #fff;
        }
        .input-dark::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }

        .btn-login {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--steel), #1e6aa0);
            color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 700; padding: 0.85rem; font-size: 0.95rem;
            width: 100%; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(42,122,184,0.35);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.5rem;
        }
        .btn-login:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(42,122,184,0.45); }

        .card-footer-link {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.28); text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.8rem; display: flex; align-items: center;
            gap: 0.4rem; transition: color 0.2s; justify-content: center;
        }
        .card-footer-link:hover { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }

        @media (max-width: 767px) { .login-card { max-width: 100%; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-wrap">

        <!-- Left info panel -->
        <div class="login-info">
            <div class="info-logo">
                <div class="info-logo-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-server"></i></div>
                <div>
                    <div class="info-logo-name">Admin Panel</div>
                    <div class="info-logo-sub">PT. Trimas Mitra Perkasa</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h2 class="info-title">Internal <span>Management</span><br>System</h2>
            <p class="info-desc">Panel administrasi eksklusif untuk tim internal PT. Trimas Mitra Perkasa. Kelola katalog produk, penawaran harga, dan data pelanggan.</p>
            <ul class="info-features">
                <li><i class="fa-solid fa-file-invoice-dollar"></i> Proses permintaan penawaran harga (RFQ)</li>
                <li><i class="fa-solid fa-boxes-stacked"></i> Kelola katalog produk & stok</li>
                <li><i class="fa-solid fa-users"></i> Pantau database pelanggan mitra</li>
                <li><i class="fa-solid fa-gauge-high"></i> Dashboard statistik transaksi</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Login card -->
        <div class="login-card">
            <div class="card-eyebrow">AKSES ADMINISTRATOR</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Secure Login</h3>
            <p class="card-sub">Internal system only · PT. Trimas Mitra Perkasa</p>

            <form action="/admin-login" method="POST">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label class="form-label-dark">Username</label>
                    <input type="text" name="username" class="input-dark" placeholder="admin" required autocomplete="off">
                </div>
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <label class="form-label-dark">Password</label>
                    <input type="password" name="password" class="input-dark" placeholder="••••••••" required>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn-login mb-4">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-lock"></i> Masuk ke Sistem
                </button>
            </form>

            <div style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); padding-top: 1.25rem;">
                <a href="/portal" class="card-footer-link">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> Portal Pelanggan
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
